<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="p-1 m-3 card text-dark bg-light-3">
            <h2 class="card-header text-center">Chat with the WWSU DJ</h2>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div id="messages-status"><div class="p-3 bs-callout bs-callout-danger shadow-4 text-light"><h4>Chat Status: Connecting...</h4>The chat system is not yet ready for use.</div></div>
                <div class="container-fluid bg-light-2 text-dark" id="messages" style="height: 360px; overflow-y: auto;">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="nickname">Nickname (Change if you want the DJ to know who you are)</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nickname" maxlength="32" placeholder="" tabindex="0">
                    <label for="themessage">Message</label>
                    <div class="bg-light text-dark">
                        <div id="themessage" class="form-control" tabindex="0" disabled></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary m-1" id="sendmessage" onclick="sendMessage(false);" tabindex="0" disabled>
                        Send Publicly
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary m-1" id="sendmessagep" onclick="sendMessage(true);" tabindex="0" disabled>
                        DM the DJ <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary m-1" id="clearchat" onclick="clearChat();" tabindex="0">
                        Clear Messages
                    </button>
                </div>
<div class="m-1 bs-callout bs-callout-info shadow-4 text-light" id="chat-subscribe" style="display: none;">
Click "subscribe" if you want push notifications when the DJ sends you a direct message. <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" onclick="OneSignal.showNativePrompt();" tabindex="0">Subscribe</button>
</div>
                <div class="p-3 bs-callout bs-callout-warning text-light shadow-2"><strong>Your IP address is logged when you send messages.</strong> Abuse of the chat system could result in being banned from the listener's corner.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>